 Movies","display_priority":3},{"logo_path":"/SPnB1qiCkYfirS2it3hZORwGVn.jpg","provider_id":2,"provider_name":"Apple TV Store","display_priority":4}]},"ZA":{"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/400136/watch?locale=ZA","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/ilR8XFZOr3e3wETQ4ZXLjXQXrts.jpg","provider_id":55,"provider_name":"ShowMax","display_priority":4}]},"ZM":{"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/400136/watch?locale=ZM","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/ilR8XFZOr3e3wETQ4ZXLjXQXrts.jpg","provider_id":55,"provider_name":"ShowMax","display_priority":7}]},"ZW":{"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/400136/watch?locale=ZW","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/ilR8XFZOr3e3wETQ4ZXLjXQXrts.jpg","provider_id":55,"provider_name":"ShowMax","display_priority":0}]}}},"wikidata_id":"Q22681637","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-22T21:58:09.42789+00:00","region":null,"main_poster":null,"images":null,"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:07:50.099+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"Evil is reborn","homepage":"https://web.archive.org/web/20171203101604/http://www.residentevilvendetta.com/","overview":"When a fearless enemy out for revenge unleashes a brutal and deadly new virus, BSAA captain Chris Redfield enlists the help of Agent Leon S. Kennedy and Professor Rebecca Chambers to bring down the death merchant and save New York City."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil - Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Resident Evil: Vendetta è un film in computer grafica diretto da Takanori Tsujimoto e uscito in versione digitale in Giappone il 27 maggio 2017.  È il terzo capitolo dopo Resident Evil: Degeneration e Resident Evil: Damnation e si colloca temporalmente tra i videogiochi Resident Evil 6 e Resident Evil 7: Biohazard.  In questo nuovo capitolo della saga ritroviamo i tre protagonisti, l'agente del BSAA Chris Redfield, la ricercatrice Rebecca Chambers e l'esperto in materia Leon Scott Kennedy. Qui i tre dovranno affrontare Glenn Arias, assieme al suo braccio destro Maria Gomez, un affascinante trafficante di armi biologiche che vuole diffondere il virus Trigger sulla città di New York a causa della morte della sua futura moglie."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: A Vingança","runtime":97,"tagline":"Vingança é um prato que se come cru.","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield, da BSAA, pede ajuda ao agente do governo Leon S. Kennedy e à professora Rebecca Chambers, do Instituto de Biotecnologia Alexander, para impedir que um mercador da morte vingativo espalhe um vírus mortal em Nova York."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"Un Film de Takanori Tsujimoto","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield, de la BSAA, cuenta con la ayuda del agente del Gobierno Leon S. Kennedy y la profesora Rebecca Chambers del Instituto Alexander de Biotecnología, para parar a un mercader de la muerte que busca venganza, y amenaza con extender un virus mortal por Nueva York."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Răul rezident: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"În a doua continuare din această franciză de animație, niște agenți luptă împotriva unui dușman răzbunător care vrea să elibereze în lume un virus letal."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://biohazard-vendetta.com","overview":"対バイオテロ組織「BSAA」のクリス・レッドフィールドは、武器密売組織の拠点に突入し探索中に国際指名手配犯グレン・アリアスと対峙するが逃してしまう。一方、元ラクーン市警の特殊部隊「S.T.A.R.S.」の一員レベッカ・チェンバースは、大学で死者が甦り、凶暴化する事件の調査、研究する中、新型ウィルスの関与を突き止め、治療薬開発に成功するが直後、研究所が何者かに襲撃される。クリスは協力を求めて新型ウィルス事件に詳しい大統領直轄のエージェント組織「DSO」所属のレオン・Ｓ・ケネディのもとへ向かい、再会した二人は、アリアスのバイオテロ阻止のためニューヨークへと向かう。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"惡靈古堡：血仇","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"隸屬生化恐怖活動組織「BSAA」的克里斯，前往搭救慘遭殭屍襲擊的警察特殊部隊 S.T.A.R.S 小組成員蕾貝卡，她因此得以撿回一命。在這次的襲擊之後，為了追補「生化恐怖活動」首腦安里亞斯，防止他危害無辜的人們，兩人同追著他前往紐約，卻不知道，又陷入另一場陰謀……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Обитель Зла: Вендетта","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Специалист B.S.A.A. Крис Редфилд помогает правительственному агенту Леону С. Кеннеди и профессору Ребекке Чемберс из Института биотехнологий. Троице придётся противостоять безумному учёному Эриасу и его армии ходячих мертвецов."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Vi følger et umage team bestående en af bioterror ekspert, en berygtet våbenhandler, en professor og en hemmelig agent der sammen skal redde New York City inden byen udslettes af en dødelig virus."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil : Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield membre de la Bioterrorism Security Assessment Alliance, convainc l'agent du gouvernement Leon S. Kennedy et le professeur Rebecca Chambers de l'Institut de Biotechnologie Alexander d'arrêter un marchant de mort en quête de vengeance prêt à libérer un virus mortel au coeur de New York."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield staat aan het hoofd van de \"BSAA\", een speciale eenheid. Samen met zijn team begeeft hij zich naar een landhuis, waar het krioelt van de zombies. De zombies zijn geïnfecteerd met een nieuw type zombievirus."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":0,"tagline":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield i Leon S. Kennedy walczą z przeważającymi siłami zombie."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"生化危机：复仇","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　BSAA的克里斯根据情报，率队突入私卖武器组织的据点——某所洋馆。在探索过程中，克里斯与国际通缉犯格伦·阿利亚斯展开对峙，结果看到难以置信的一幕并被对方逃走。另一方面，现任大学教授的瑞贝卡则在调查研究“死者苏醒并凶暴化”的离奇事件。在调查中，瑞贝卡发现了新型病毒与此事有关，并开发出了解药。但是研究所突然遭到袭击，危难关头在赶来的克里斯的帮助下，瑞贝卡才九死一生。此次袭击过后，克里斯和瑞贝卡找到了里昂，隶属于美国总统直属的DSO组织的他是最了解此次新型病毒事件的人物。格伦·阿里亚斯的真正目的是生化恐怖，再度相会的克里斯与里昂则和瑞贝卡一起，为了阻止对方的阴谋而奔赴纽约……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"레지던트 이블: 벤데타","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"대 바이오 테러 조직 'BSAA'의 크리스 레드 필드는 정보를 바탕으로 불법무기 밀매 조직의 거점 인 수수께끼의 양옥에 잠입한다.탐색 하던 중 크리스는 국제 수배자인 \"글렌 아리아스\"와 대치하는 도중 믿기힘든 광경을 보게되는 한편, 라쿤 시경의 특수 부대 'STARS'의 일원이었던 레베카 챔버스는 현재 대학 교수로 \"사망자가 되살아 난다\" 라는 이상한 사건의 조사, 연구을 하고 있었다.사건의 조사를 통해 \"신형 바이러스\"가 관계하고있는 것을 밝혀내고 그녀는 치료제의 개발에 성공. 그 직후, 연구소가 누군가에게 습격을 받고 레베카는 죽음의 위험에 노출되어 버리지만, 다행히 달려온 크리스들에 의해 구출된다. 이 습격 후 크리스와 레베카는 미국 대통령 직할 에이전트 조직 \"DSO\"에 소속 된 레온 S 케네디에게로 ... 그는이 신형 바이러스가 관련된 사건을 가장 잘 아는 인물이었다  다시만나게 된 \"크리스와 레온\" 은 국제 테러수배자인 \"글렌 아리아스\"의 진정한 목적이 \"바이오 테러\"라고 생각한  두사람은 레베카와 함께 그의 목적을 저지하고 사람들을 구하기 위해 그를 쫓아 뉴욕으로 향한다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Uma equipe do Exército Mexicano supervisionada pelo capitão da BSAA, Chris Redfield, investiga uma mansão ligada a uma operação de contrabando da B.O.W., que está infestada de zumbis infetados com uma nova cepa viral. Lá ele encontra Glenn Arias, um traficante do mercado negro procurado pela Interpol, mas Arias foge quando a mansão explode. Ele logo é acompanhado por uma das conselheiras da BSAA, a Dra. Rebecca Chambers, que começa a desenvolver medicamentos para combater o vírus encontrado na mansão. O laboratório é atacado por um dos cúmplices de Arias no final de sua pesquisa, e Chris a salva da infeção. Após o ataque, eles chamam a atenção do agente da DSO, Leon S. Kennedy. Concluindo que Arias está envolvido em um próximo ataque terrorista, eles vão para Nova York para encontrá-lo antes que ele possa ocorrer."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"A Kaptár: Vendetta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield, a BSAA rangos tisztje Leon S. Kennedy és Prof. Rebecca Chambers segítségére szorul az Alexander Institute of Biotechnology-tól. Együtt meg kell állítaniuk egy mániákus őrültet, aki bosszúból halálos vírust akar elszabadítni New Yorkban.."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"BSAA-ryhmän Chris Redfield värvää avukseen agentti Leon S. Kennedyn ja professori Rebecca Chambersin pysäyttäkseen tappavaa virusta levittävän kuolemankauppiaan."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"ผีชีวะ ล้างบางเชื้อคลั่ง","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หน่วยงาน BSAA “คริส เรดฟิลด์” ได้ทำการสืบสวนหาสาเหตุการแพร่กระจายไวรัสชนิดใหม่ ที่ทำให้คนที่ตายไปแล้วคืนชีพขึ้นมาและบ้าคลั่งทำร้ายคนอื่น โดยมีเบื้องหลังคือพ่อค้าอาวุธชีวภาพ “เกลน แอรีส” ชายผู้หมายจะครองตลาดค้าอาวุธชีวภาพด้วยการเก็บตกเหล่าเชื้อไวรัสของบ.ไทรเซล และอัมเบรลล่า โดยไวรัสชนิดนี้ นอกจากทำให้คนกลายเป็นซอมบี้แล้ว เขายังสามารถโปรแกรมให้มันแยกแยะมิตรหรือศัตรู และมันก็ใช้ได้ผลดีกับพวก B.O.W. อีกด้วย ด้วยความช่วยเหลือของ “รีเบคก้า แชมเบอร์ส” นักวิจัยของ BSAA ทำให้การสืบสวนของคริสคืบหน้าไม่น้อย แต่คริสก็ยังเสียลูกน้องในทีมไปอีกเขาจึงมาขอความร่วมมือกับเจ้าหน้าที่ความมั่นคงของชา ติ “ลีออน สก๊อต เคเนดี้” มาช่วยอีกแรงในการหยุดไวรัส"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"„Vendetta“  ist nach „Resident Evil 6“ angesiedelt und handelt von Chris Redfield, einem Agenten der Bio-Terrorism Security Assessment Alliance (BSAA), der sich mit dem US-Regierungsagenten Leon S. Kennedy und der Professorin Rebecca Chambers vom Alexander Institute Of Biotechnology zusammenschließt, um den schurkischen Glenn Arias aufzuhalten. Arias ist ein rachsüchtiger Waffenhändler, der plant, ein tödliches Virus in New York freizusetzen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Venganza","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield reclama la ayuda de Leon S. Kennedy y Rebecca Chambers para impedir que un mercader de la muerte, con ánimo de venganza, propague un virus mortal en Nueva York."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ο πράκτορας ασφαλείας κατά της βιολογικής τρομοκρατίας Chris Redfield στρατολογεί τον κυβερνητικό πράκτορα Leon S. Kennedy και την καθηγήτρια Rebecca Chambers από το Ίδρυμα Βιοτεχνολογίας Alexander για να το βοηθήσουν να σταματήσει έναν παρανοϊκό έμπορο θανάτου που σκοπεύει να ελευθερώσει έναν θανατηφόρο ιό στη New York."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendeta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Keď bezohľadný protivník v túžbe po odplate vypustí nebezpečný smrteľný vírus, kapitán protiteroristickej jednotky Chris Redfield požiada o pomoc agenta Leona S. Kennedyho a profesorku Rebeccu Chambers, aby spoločnými silami zastavili obchodníka so smrťou a zachránili New York."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"BSAA-agenten Chris Redfield tar hjälp av agent Leon S. Kennedy och professor Rebecca Chambers för att hindra en kriminell biovapenhandlare från att sprida ett dödligt virus."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Заразно зло: Вендета","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Сътрудникът на организация за борба с биотероризма Крис Редфийлд, прониква в тайнствен замък, който съгласно информацията, се явява база на контрабандисти на оръжие. В хода на разследването Крис се сблъсква с Глен Ариас, престъпник обявен за международно издирване, и става свидетел на странна ситуация, в която губи Ариас."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendeta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Když bezohledný protivník v touze po odplatě vypustí nebezpečný smrtelný virus, kapitán protiteroristické jednotky Chris Redfield požádá o pomoc agenta Leona S. Kennedyho a profesorku Rebeccu Chambers, aby společnými silami zastavili obchodníka se smrtí a zachránili New York."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"האויב שבפנים: נקמת דם","runtime":0,"tagline":"נקמה.","homepage":"","overview":"כריס רדפילד מגייס את עזרתם של ליאון ס. קנדי ורבקה צ'יימברס לעצור מתנקש, מתוך נקמה, מלהפיץ וירוס קטלני בניו יורק."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"الشر المقيم - الثأر","runtime":0,"tagline":"ريزيدنت ايفل ، بايوهازارد ، الشر المقيم ، الثأر ، الانتقام","homepage":"","overview":"ريزدنت إيفل: الثأرهو فيلم رعب ثلاثي الأبعاد من إنتاج شركة كابكوم وتوزيع شركة سوني بيكتشرز إنترتينمنت اليابانية ومن إخراج تاكانوري تسوجيموتو وإنتاج هيرويوكي كوباياشيز وهو الجزء الثالث صدر في 27 مايو 2017\r القصة :\r “الشر المقيم :الثأر”  حول “كريس ريدفيلد” الذى يطلب المساعدة من “ليون إس كينيدي” و”ريبيكا تشامبرز” لايقاف مسيرة الموت المستمرة مع انتقام من انتشار فيروس مميت في نيويورك"},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Vendetta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"BSAA Chris Redfield, Alexander Institute of Biotechnology'den hükümet temsilcisi Leon S. Kennedy ve Profesör Rebecca Chambers'ın New York'a ölümcül bir virüs salmayı amaçlayan ölüm tacirlerini durdurmaları için yardım sağlamaya çalışacaktır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Оселя зла: Вендета","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Спеціаліст B.S.A.A. Кріс Редфілд допомагає урядовому агенту Леону С. Кеннеді та професору Ребеці Чемберс з Інституту біотехнологій. Трійці доведеться протистояти шаленому вченому Еріасу та його армії ходячих мерців."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"生化危機：血仇殺戮","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"隸屬生化恐怖主義安全評估聯盟「BSAA」的克里斯‧瑞德菲爾 (Chris Redfield)，依照某個情報前往一個武器走私組織據點的神秘大屋中。克里斯在探索時與國際通緝犯葛倫．艾瑞亞斯 (Glenn Arias) 對峙，期間更目睹難以置信的情景，結果被艾瑞亞斯逃跑了。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil : Vendetta","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chris Redfield membre de la Bioterrorism Security Assessment Alliance, convainc l'agent du gouvernement Leon S. Kennedy et le professeur Rebecca Chambers de l'Institut de Biotechnologie Alexander d'arrêter un marchant de mort en quête de vengeance prêt à libérer un virus mortel au coeur de New York."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Nevidno zlo: Maščevanje","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"BSAA Chris Redfield prosi za pomoč vladnega agenta Leona S. Kennedyja in profesorico Rebecco Chambers z Alexanderovega inštituta za biotehnologijo, da bi trgovcu s smrtjo preprečili maščevalno širjenje smrtonosnega virusa v New Yorku."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Vùng Đất Quỷ Dữ: Nợ Máu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Resident Evil: Vendetta xoay quanh bộ ba Chris Redfield, Leon Scoot Kennedy và Rebecca Chambers có mặt ở thành phố New York để ngăn cản cuộc tấn công khủng bố sinh học đang bùng phát với zombie cũng như nhiều sinh vật đột biến quái dị hơn. Âm mưu phá hoại thành phố được thực hiện bởi nhân vật phản diện mang tên Glenn Arias."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Absoliutus Blogis: Vendetta","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Animacinis specialiųjų efektų ir įtempto siužeto filmas „Absoliutus blogis: kraujo kerštas“ - tai dar viena legendinės zombių sagos dalis, kurioje sugrįžta legendiniai personažai - Krisas Redfildas ir Leonas Kenedis, fanams geriau pažįstami iš kompiuterinių žaidimų serijos. Krisas su Leonu, kartu su buvusios S.T.A.R.S organizacijos nare Rebeka Čembers siekia bet kokia kaina sustabdyti mirtį sėjantį ginklų prekeivį, kuris kėsinasi visą Niujorką užkrėsti mirtinu virusu, gyvuosius paverčiančiu mirusiais ir kraujo ištroškusiais padarais."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Resident Evil: Osveta","runtime":0,"tagline":"Pripremite se za najsmrtonosniju osvetu do sada.","homepage":"","overview":"Elitni agent Chris Redfield suočava se s novom, smrtonosnom prijetnjom koja potječe od trgovca oružjem Glenna Ariasa. Arias planira smrtonosni teroristički napad u New Yorku koristeći novorazvijeni virus. Chris udružuje snage s agenticom FBI-a Rebeccom Chambers i agentom Leonom S. Kennedyjem kako bi zaustavili Ariasa. Njihova istraga vodi ih od napuštene vile u Louisiani do ulica New Yorka, gdje moraju spriječiti globalnu katastrofu. No, Arias ima osobnu motivaciju za svoje postupke, a prošlost njegovih žrtava skriva mračnu tajnu. Hoće li uspjeti zaustaviti prijetnju prije nego bude prekasno?"},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Nezūdošais ļaunums: Atriebe","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"اهریمن خاموش انتقام","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"اهریمن مقیم : انتقام ، کریس ردفیلد از لیان اسکات کندی و ربکا چمبر درخواست کمک می کند تا جلوی فردی را بگیرند که قصد دارد برای گرفتن انتقام، ویروسی کشنده را در شهر نیویورک پخش کند..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":133121,"adult":false,"title":"Resident Evil: Damnation","video":false,"overview":"U.S. federal agent Leon S. Kennedy sneaks into the \"East Slavic Republic\" to verify rumors that Bio-Organic Weapons (BOWs) are being used in the country's civil war, which the U.S. and Russia are making preparations to jointly intervene in. Right after his infiltration, the U.S. government orders him to leave immediately. Determined to uncover the truth, Leon ignores the order and enters the battlefield to end the chain of tragedies caused by the BOWs.","genre_ids":[28,16,878,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6288,"vote_count":973,"poster_path":"/zkHSURVCrt7rpvDDgUXO75CV1v4.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-25","vote_average":6.893,"backdrop_path":"/xbjOkrAaT4CAIrNJ38oQSBomHvg.jpg","original_title":"バイオハザード ダムネーション","original_language":"ja"},{"id":13648,"adult":false,"title":"Resident Evil: Degeneration","video":false,"overview":"Leon S. Kennedy and Claire Redfield must battle a rogue warrior seeking revenge after unleashing the deadly G-Virus, whilst a mutated monster goes on a rampage.","genre_ids":[16,27,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.769,"vote_count":1152,"poster_path":"/1x5OaFOo38JAwR5yXxeuvQg3VWH.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-13","vote_average":6.819,"backdrop_path":"/3JgfNUCoN6pyXlO7wZOJ4PgQgW3.jpg","original_title":"バイオハザード：ディジェネレーション","original_language":"ja"},{"id":497467,"adult":false,"title":"Biohazard 4: Incubate","video":true,"overview":"A special CGI film made-for DVD summarizing the story of the Resident Evil 4 game, excluding a couple of scenes for narrative consistency.  Leon S. Kennedy, now a federal agent, is hired to rescue the president's daughter from a sinister cult.","genre_ids":[27,28,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6218,"vote_count":40,"poster_path":"/aEXC9SmF3j6fWw3bIQTCe9DNqZQ.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-28","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/6jnokb9eEklqZlmlzNMiaYnmyeK.jpg","original_title":"バイオハザード4 Incubate","original_language":"ja"},{"id":345915,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time in Venice","video":false,"overview":"Steve Ford is a private detective in Venice Beach, Calif., who's good with the ladies, bad with the punches and wild about his dog Buddy. When local thugs steal Buddy, Ford turns to Spyder, their devious leader, and forges an unlikely alliance. With help from his best friend, Steve pulls out the big guns to retrieve Spyder's stolen cash and cocaine and save Buddy.","genre_ids":[28,35,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3695,"vote_count":696,"poster_path":"/5rr7tQfzS0ARqEea3W9SNSFGRzb.jpg","release_date":"2017-06-08","vote_average":5.231,"backdrop_path":"/wJQowXYcpcujDJA2NAM1GSCZtM2.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time in Venice","original_language":"en"},{"id":235704,"adult":false,"title":"Commitment","video":false,"overview":"The son of a North Korean spy decides to follow in his father's footsteps to protect his little sister.","genre_ids":[28,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.6605,"vote_count":137,"poster_path":"/ybM400b3vesnoNzOlTlAmHeEYPq.jpg","release_date":"2013-11-05","vote_average":7.212,"backdrop_path":"/alo20exRRwPj1vhqrjbmaee9op9.jpg","original_title":"동창생","original_language":"ko"},{"id":550518,"adult":false,"title":"South Wind","video":false,"overview":"A story about Petar Maraš, a Belgrade criminal in his late twenties, whose one reckless move causes an avalanche of events that will greatly affect the lives of those around him.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3889,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/4pi5trlxslcIdlTZ8ZMhUtBIGQE.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-23","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/4rgwjCz2H4DOiq0rd1bzjTdAWkr.jpg","original_title":"Јужни ветар","original_language":"sr"},{"id":17740,"adult":false,"title":"Powder Blue","video":false,"overview":"On the gritty streets of LA, the destinies of four people desperate for connection and redemption are about to collide.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.9995,"vote_count":247,"poster_path":"/o1wQcqOoQQF7tt1HijnmQRLjTo4.jpg","release_date":"2009-05-08","vote_average":6.113,"backdrop_path":"/tIgy95Ai5vYv7AS0iu4DlFJQL8u.jpg","original_title":"Powder Blue","original_language":"en"},{"id":257444,"adult":false,"title":"The Boy","video":false,"overview":"An intimate portrait of a 9 year old sociopath as he discovers his taste for killing.","genre_ids":[18,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6376,"vote_count":194,"poster_path":"/vqHJ7mV2EmVSO7cxb4SN49vRWgu.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-14","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/seSEfSOzDSMC3FPivmiD7sVV8To.jpg","original_title":"The Boy","original_language":"en"},{"id":496200,"adult":false,"title":"The Demon of the Andes","video":false,"overview":"El Demonio de los Andes, directed by Palito Ortega Matute, is based on the Andean myth of the Jarjacha, a demonic character set on destroying everyone it comes across.  The legend of the Jajacha has been passed down from generation to generation. Ortega Matute spoke to people who were told about it by their parents, who had been told the tale by their parents. He also listened to accounts from people who say they’ve seen the demon with their own eyes.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0357,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/wAU8RCEbuF5RvB3ToKS15xfKGMi.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-28","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"El Demonio de los Andes","original_language":"en"},{"id":1017138,"adult":false,"title":"[REC]: Horror Without Pause","video":false,"overview":"The horror film [REC] — directed by Jaume Balagueró and Paco Plaza, and released in 2007 — was an unprecedented triumph for Spanish fantasy cinema. Fifteen years later, those responsible for the creation and worldwide success of this cinematic milestone decode its keys and resurrect the myth.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6418,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/jme3yUGa0pVvYXOBTQxldfvny0n.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-28","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/e5ZMGCPw4HWhA56LD3wqVlmSz3g.jpg","original_title":"[REC]: terror sin pausa","original_language":"es"},{"id":435880,"adult":false,"title":"Warriors of the Dawn","video":false,"overview":"A crown prince emerges as a leader during the war between Korea and Japan in 1592.","genre_ids":[10752,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6778,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/mxLhHLXouZ8IMdYjFLaoxuQecK5.jpg","release_date":"2017-05-31","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/1yMt58XEJMNxqrl4y9dTVMArKcb.jpg","original_title":"대립군","original_language":"ko"},{"id":122924,"adult":false,"title":"One in the Chamber","video":false,"overview":"A seasoned assassin plays both sides in a Russian gang war and becomes the target of an unknown enemy.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7275,"vote_count":165,"poster_path":"/QQu9v0AwjO0fIj4pnpiBYhGk0T.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-21","vote_average":5.527,"backdrop_path":"/4YubhOmbxTSdnMBhjQGngd7TSao.jpg","original_title":"One in the Chamber","original_language":"en"},{"id":272691,"adult":false,"title":"Sea Fog","video":false,"overview":"A fishing-boat crew takes on a dangerous commission to smuggle a group of illegal immigrants from China to Korea.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0207,"vote_count":173,"poster_path":"/gnqv8hSNKfNZXKsJXMxJocDVGK7.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-13","vote_average":6.844,"backdrop_path":"/xh6e4z9vawuXUt6G2MHkANQervv.jpg","original_title":"해무","original_language":"ko"},{"id":242546,"adult":false,"title":"Bayonetta: Bloody Fate","video":false,"overview":"Bayonetta is an ancient witch who awakens from a five hundred-year slumber with no memory of her life. Armed with a gun in each limb, she embarks on a journey to rediscover her past, defeating all bloodthirsty angels that stand in her way.","genre_ids":[16,28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5737,"vote_count":120,"poster_path":"/dfg7dqm0YX16D6QYDKDdh3Qi930.jpg","release_date":"2013-11-23","vote_average":6.85,"backdrop_path":"/qfTGzbtqTBhz1krD0Zh5bCg5xlf.jpg","original_title":"ベヨネッタ ブラッディフェイト","original_language":"ja"},{"id":419706,"adult":false,"title":"Mary","video":false,"overview":"A struggling family buys an old ship at auction with high hopes of starting a charter business, only to discover her horrifying secrets on the isolated open waters.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8609,"vote_count":225,"poster_path":"/cdcyHzqqBrzPGJFVH29ONnzsV6I.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-19","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/3g6Aznrs25uQxxxqNiJ2KfCe7lU.jpg","original_title":"Mary","original_language":"en"},{"id":1083862,"adult":false,"title":"Resident Evil: Death Island","video":false,"overview":"In San Francisco, Jill Valentine is dealing with a zombie outbreak and a new T-Virus, Leon Kennedy is on the trail of a kidnapped DARPA scientist, and Claire Redfield is investigating a monstrous fish that is killing whales in the bay. Joined by Chris Redfield and Rebecca Chambers, they discover the trail of clues from their separate cases all converge on the same location, Alcatraz Island, where a new evil has taken residence and awaits their arrival.","genre_ids":[28,16,878,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.432,"vote_count":1080,"poster_path":"/qayga07ICNDswm0cMJ8P3VwklFZ.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-22","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/7drO1kYgQ0PnnU87sAnBEphYrSM.jpg","original_title":"バイオハザード：デスアイランド","original_language":"ja"},{"id":299824,"adult":false,"title":"Mojin: The Lost Legend","video":false,"overview":"Three tomb raiders retire from their roles and move to New York to enjoy the rest of their lives. However, they are asked to resume duty in order to find out the reason behind the loss of a loved one.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3793,"vote_count":257,"poster_path":"/supoIHkh3dzDi1XmvK8tgGlkGNS.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-18","vote_average":6.247,"backdrop_path":"/6ilMT6VCADu5F1Xr9LjiVxQSXPp.jpg","original_title":"寻龙诀","original_language":"zh"},{"id":531145,"adult":false,"title":"Boarding School","video":false,"overview":"When troubled 12-year-old Jacob Felsen is sent away to boarding school, he enters every kid’s worst nightmare: a creepy old mansion, deserted except for six other teenage misfits and two menacing and mysterious teachers. As events become increasingly horrific, Jacob must conquer his fears to find the strength to survive.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7221,"vote_count":232,"poster_path":"/lun3G1IU6AYgXlXP649amULMPpv.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-30","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/f0eeCDOR8VkyKYtKSLpMWtxtec6.jpg","original_title":"Boarding School","original_language":"en"},{"id":15268,"adult":false,"title":"Street Fighter: The Legend of Chun-Li","video":false,"overview":"When a teenager, Chun-Li witnesses the kidnapping of her father by wealthy crime lord M. Bison. When she grows up, she goes on a quest for vengeance and becomes the famous crime-fighter of the Street Fighter universe.","genre_ids":[28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4032,"vote_count":483,"poster_path":"/lbNemoc9bRIAIVck0e2cv1cgftN.jpg","release_date":"2009-02-27","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":"/ee6AZ0B098pTSbQH6AwVZCT6Pag.jpg","original_title":"Street Fighter: The Legend of Chun-Li","original_language":"en"},{"id":7737,"adult":false,"title":"Resident Evil: Extinction","video":false,"overview":"Years after the Racoon City catastrophe, survivors travel across the Nevada desert, hoping to make it to Alaska. Alice joins the caravan and their fight against hordes of zombies and the evil Umbrella Corp.","genre_ids":[27,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7079,"vote_count":4464,"poster_path":"/6yaLr7Ymg5cvbtSVi5hHwBKx35I.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-20","vote_average":6.304,"backdrop_path":"/ptA3Mooo0jYy2LHLIZicDkbbP7r.jpg","original_title":"Resident Evil: Extinction","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":462115,"adult":false,"title":"Dead Trigger","video":false,"overview":"2021 - 5 years after the outbreak of a mysterious virus that turned humans into bloodthirsty, undead beasts much of the world’s population has been decimated. When governments were unable to keep the disease at bay, the Contagion Special Unit was formed with the toughest soldiers and best specialists to fight the infected. Because of the rapidly decreasing number of soldiers, a popular online video game Dead Trigger that mirrors the terrifying events was created. The best efforts of the gamers are monitored by the CSU who recruit the highest rated zombie killers. The young recruits are called “Dead Triggers”. The movie follows a group of young recruits who must travel to the origin of the outbreak to find a missing team of scientists who were searching for a cure.","genre_ids":[28,27],"popularity":0.6337,"vote_count":50,"poster_path":"/uI2c30FyDEeBaa7Ka7tZYH344tC.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-19","vote_average":3.7,"backdrop_path":"/rZwmA9WtrntPnaR8urEPIYoI8Hy.jpg","original_title":"Dead Trigger","original_language":"en"},{"id":1250695,"adult":false,"title":"Zomburbia","video":false,"overview":"A 1950s housewife must defend herself against the zombie apocalypse armed with a spatula, egg beaters, a blender, and a rolling pin.","genre_ids":[35,27],"popularity":0.4111,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/49BfkJY2QbSRMpNfeUGROcEq0aY.jpg","release_date":"2017-05-26","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/8pIzbEYjrd6uEDWi1ArXliKBwAL.jpg","original_title":"Zomburbia","original_language":"en"},{"id":652754,"adult":false,"title":"Dragon Ball Z Side Story: Plan to Eradicate the Saiyans","video":false,"overview":"Dr. Raichi is one of the only survivors of the Tuffles, a race that once lived on Planet Plant before the coming of the Saiyans. The Saiyans not only massacred the entire Tuffle race, but also stole their technology and conquered the planet, renaming it Planet Vegeta in honor of their king. Raichi managed to escape with a capsule and found refuge on the Dark Planet, a world at the end of the universe. His only wish is to eradicate the last remaining Saiyans.","genre_ids":[28,12,16],"popularity":2.9305,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/3sb7LPrIrNMp8ZlsUSEhNwhUpU0.jpg","release_date":"1993-09-23","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/cot2CeGP8ir9CqBoatCmsUNOyIM.jpg","original_title":"ドラゴンボールZ外伝 サイヤ人絶滅計画","original_language":"ja"},{"id":652837,"adult":false,"title":"Josee, the Tiger and the Fish","video":false,"overview":"With dreams of diving abroad, Tsuneo gets a job assisting Josee, an artist whose imagination takes her far beyond her wheelchair. But when the tide turns against them, they push each other to places they never thought possible, and inspire a love fit for a storybook.","genre_ids":[16,18,10749],"popularity":2.6184,"vote_count":568,"poster_path":"/z1D8xi9x4uEhyFruo7uEHXUMD4K.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-25","vote_average":8.272,"backdrop_path":"/521koHpCyK6ZeNpEAvPAuC75cJ5.jpg","original_title":"ジョゼと虎と魚たち","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1250852,"adult":false,"title":"Geethanjali Malli Vachindi","video":false,"overview":"A group of boisterous artists come to film a horror movie in a seemingly haunted bungalow but their plans are soon derailed by intercepting ghosts and spirits inhabiting the premises.","genre_ids":[35,27],"popularity":0.284,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/d7qcKJjVyEKKIFuwAAqhjb9RASQ.jpg","release_date":"2024-04-11","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/tjinNF7YNzXMUjCXu5tG4XNHstW.jpg","original_title":"గీతాంజలి మళ్లీ వచ్చింది","original_language":"te"},{"id":1250784,"adult":false,"title":"Kuramerukagari","video":false,"overview":"A young cartographer must unearth the secrets of her maze-like town to save its citizens from mysterious sinkholes.","genre_ids":[16,18,9648],"popularity":0.6909,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/jr59za0cZFzt3mHt4VfIfoOxzEC.jpg","release_date":"2024-04-12","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/fsgGP4ZzPAUSFGu9No3upiw9FLh.jpg","original_title":"クラメルカガリ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1235424,"adult":false,"title":"Pui Pui Molcar the Movie: MOLMAX","video":false,"overview":"The story begins with the emergence of the first high-tech molcar in Molcity, with drivers beginning to ride state-of-the-art AI-driven Molcars. Potato and friends get involved in a chase between a mysterious organization and a Molcar AI named Cannon, and are saved by a talented driver. Potato finds out that the driver is in search of his missing Molcar, and gets the idea to use Cannon's AI functionality to help with the search.","genre_ids":[16,10751,878],"popularity":0.695,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/hFaLQGnlY7REAG9WNMWyZaqcBeJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-29","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/pe3oRebZOwhi6FFX0kA0jfPZhzX.jpg","original_title":"PUI PUI モルカー ザ・ムービー MOLMAX","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1235451,"adult":false,"title":"A Few Moments of Cheers","video":false,"overview":"High schooler Asaya Kanata throws himself into creating music videos. One night, he is stunned by the voice of a woman performing 